==German==

===Etymology===
''Kakao'' is in this case an euphemism for ''[[Kacke]]'' (Duden Herkunftswörterbuch 3rd ed.)

===Idiom===
'''[[durch]] [[den]] [[Kakao]] [[ziehen]]'''
# (''idiomatic'') To [[slate]] somebody or something.

